Package hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui.element.base

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GuiClickable<T extends GuiClickable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can be clicked.
    GuiClickable.ClickedAction<T extends GuiClickable<T>>
    The handler of the clicked action.
    GuiColorable<T extends GuiColorable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can be colored.
    GuiEditable<T extends GuiEditable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can be optionally interacted with by viewers.
    GuiElement<T extends GuiElement<T>>
    The base class for GUI elements.
    GuiHeightSettable<T extends GuiHeightSettable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that has a modifiable height.
    GuiOrientable<T extends GuiOrientable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can be oriented both vertically and horizontally.
    GuiProgressable<T extends GuiProgressable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that contains a continuous, non-discrete bar.
    GuiTextable<T extends GuiTextable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can display text.
    GuiTooltipable<T extends GuiTooltipable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can display a tooltip when hovered over.
    GuiTransparentable<T extends GuiTransparentable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that can have transparency applied.
    GuiWidthSettable<T extends GuiWidthSettable<T>>
    Represents a GuiElement that has a modifiable width.
